_sText:
Infamous DUGA-3 (a.k.a Russian Woodpecker) over the horizon radar from Chernobyl Exclusion Zone became a target for terrorists.
Terrorists aims to take down big antennas of DUGA-3 and make mini-earthquake which will make the radioactive particles go up into the air from the ground. Powerful enough to poison whole eastern Europe. Counter-terrorist must prevent that by eleminating terrorists.
